  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raven Tear is a stylized co-op adventure (4 players) in a small open world with horror elements. Evil has gripped the small town of \"Raven Tear\", you - brave hunters, must take your faithful dog and your excellent car, turn up the radio to go on a journey through the locations and drive them all back to the underworld. Grow vegetables, catch fish, earn money for equipment and arrange a safari for monsters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ATTENTION:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Due to our mistake, the game is not marked as ''Early Access'', but - the game is still in active development.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raven Tear is a stylized co-op adventure (4 players) in a small open world with horror elements. Evil has gripped the small town of \"Raven Tear\", you - brave hunters, must take your faithful dog and your excellent car, turn up the radio to go on a journey through the locations and drive them all back to the underworld. Grow vegetables, catch fish, earn money for equipment and arrange a safari for monsters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ATTENTION:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Due to our mistake, the game is not marked as ''Early Access'', but - the game is still in active development.</p>",
